div.font:
template method is design pattern is about defining a skeleton algorithm which means an algorithm that won't chanage at all, but there are some gaps in it waiting for some other implementations that are required be filled in so they need have implementations in the subclasses and these methods are abstract methods.
and it maybe need some other methods that can be filled in but if u didn't want to fill them in, there is no problem u
either can implement them or let the default implementations for them, and these methods are called hooks or virtual methods
